                        </ph><cite ixia_locid="247"><ph ixia_locid="248"><xref href="jow1425583896631.xml" ixia_locid="249"/></ph></cite>. The
                        available options are <nameliteral ixia_locid="59">static</nameliteral> or
                            <nameliteral ixia_locid="60">disabled</nameliteral>.</p -->
                    <p ixia_locid="56">(Shown only when the <uicontrol ixia_locid="197">Network
                            Type</uicontrol> is set to <nameliteral ixia_locid="57">data</nameliteral>) The method for assigning an IP address to the
                        interface for use with VXLAN networks. <draft-comment author="jmaran" ixia_locid="278">RC
                            XREF: I have updated this xref to a live link (and corrected source doc
                            reference) but xrefs are not recommended in referable content topics.
                            Suggest removing the xref or eliminating the text from referable
                            content.</draft-comment>For more information about VXLAN networks, see
                            <ph ixia_locid="279" otherprops="printonly"><cite ixia_locid="280">Titanium Server System
                                Administration: </cite></ph><cite ixia_locid="281"><ph ixia_locid="282"><xref href="jow1425583896631.xml" ixia_locid="283"/></ph></cite>.</p>
                    <dl>
                        <dlentry ixia_locid="61">
                            <dt ixia_locid="62">Disabled</dt>
                            <dd ixia_locid="63">
                                <p ixia_locid="64">Do not assign an IPv4 address.</p>
                            </dd>
                        </dlentry>
                        <dlentry ixia_locid="198">
                            <dt ixia_locid="199">Static</dt>
                            <dd ixia_locid="200">
                                <p ixia_locid="201">Use a static IPv4 address.</p>
                            </dd>
                        </dlentry>
                        <dlentry ixia_locid="202">
                            <dt ixia_locid="203">Pool</dt>
                            <dd ixia_locid="204">
                                <p ixia_locid="205"><draft-comment author="jowens" ixia_locid="206">US65058
                                        added</draft-comment>Use an address from a pool of IPv4
                                    addresses that has been defined and associated with the data
                                    interface.</p>
                            </dd>
                        </dlentry>
                    </dl>
                </dd>
            </dlentry>
            <dlentry ixia_locid="207">
                <dt ixia_locid="208">IPv4 Address Pool</dt>
                <dd ixia_locid="209">
                    <p ixia_locid="210">(Shown only when the <uicontrol ixia_locid="211">IPv4 Addressing Mode</uicontrol> is set to
                            <nameliteral ixia_locid="212">pool</nameliteral>) The pool from which to assign an IPv4
                        address.</p>
                </dd>
            </dlentry>
